** MATERIALS
**
** The shear nonlinearity coefficients used here for testing are not
** the values recommended for this material. They are used here for
** testing purposes only. The recommended values for this material are
** provided in IM7-8552-C3D-25sv.inp and are based on fitting the Ramberg-
** Osgood expression to test data.
